<h1><a href="http://thinkprogress.org/health/2014/01/16/3172071/jimmy-carter-guinea-worm/">For The First Time Since 1979, The World Is On The Verge Of Eradicating An Infectious Disease</a></h1>

<div class="post">

<p class="timestamp">
	<span class="byline"> by <a href="http://thinkprogress.org/?person=smukherjee">Sy Mukherjee</a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=the_sy_guy"><img src="http://thinkprogress.org/wp-content/plugins//cap-byline/bird_blue_16.png" class="twitter-bird"></a> </span><span class="posted-on">Posted on <time class="published" datetime="January 16, 2014 at 11:21 am">January 16, 2014 at 11:21 am</time>&nbsp;<time class="updated" datetime="January 16, 2014 at 3:11 pm">Updated: January 16, 2014 at 3:11 pm</time></span></p>


